<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
<title>身份证-居住信息认证</title>
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
<meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black">
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
<meta http-equiv="cleartype" content="on">
<link href="../../css/KaNiu/style.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<link href="../../css/KaNiu/gennal.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body class="f5">
<div class="content">
    <p class="file_tt">居住信息</p>
    <form id="form" name="form" method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="/InterFace/kaniuFace.ashx">
    <div class="add_bank wid_13">
        <ul>
            <li><b>现居住地</b>
                <p class="winwzwz"><i class="mapimg"></i>{$:jzrz_adress htmlencode=”true”}</p>
            </li>
            <li class="bbomnone"><b>详细地址</b>
                <input name="xx_adr" id="xx_adr" type="text" placeholder="请输入您的详细居住地址">
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="file_ss">身份证信息</p>
    <div>
        <div class="file_up pt40 borderno" style="max-height: 945px;">
            <div class="jbzl">
                <p class="upnr upleft fl"><i></i><span class="ft">上传身份证正面</span>
                    <input type="file" id="file01" name="file" multiple accept="image/jpg, image/jpeg, image/png" >
                    <b id="preview01"><img id="imghead01" src=''></b>
                </p>
                <p class="upnr upright fr"><i></i><span class="ft">上传身份证反面</span>
                    <input type="file" id="file02" name="file" multiple accept="image/jpg, image/jpeg, image/png" >
                    <b id="preview02"><img id="imghead02" src=''></b>
                </p>
                <p class="upnr upbom fl"><i class="peo"></i><b class="hft">请确保身份证<br>
                    姓名号码清晰</b><i class="camera"></i><span class="ft">上传手持身份证照片</span>
                    <input type="file" id="file03" name="file" multiple accept="image/jpg, image/jpeg, image/png" >
                    <b id="preview03"><img id="imghead03" src=''></b>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    </form>
    <div class="both bank_bom">
        <p class="tips"><img src="../../images/KaNiu/input_01.png"><span>您所填写的银行卡必须是您本人的，图片格式暂时支持jpg，jpeg，png　单张图片最大不超过1M。</span></p>
        <p><input id="subpeo" name="" class="" type="button" value="填好了" disabled="disabled" onclick="checkfile()"></p>
    </div>
</div>


<script src="../../js/KaNiu/jquery-1.10.2.7l.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="../../js/KaNiu/imghelper.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var file01 = document.getElementById("file01");
	file01.onchange = function () {
		return filechange.apply(this, [this.files, "imghead01", "front", "/InterFace/ValidateCreid.ashx"])
	};
</script>
</body>
</html>
